results.title: Live. Laugh. Love. Lava Bead Essential Oil Diffuser Bracelet
results.description:
This bracelet features the mantra - "Live. Laugh. Love." This aromatherapy bracelet features not only a beautiful quote band, but also fuchsia glass beads, and 2 black lava beads for your essential oil diffusing pleasure. This is a stretch bracelet measuring approximately 7", 7.5", or 8" (please choose a size from the drop-down menu).



Essential Oil Application:

Only apply essential oils to the lava beads.

Place 1-2 drops of your favorite essential oil on each bead.

I find it easiest to place the necklace on a flat surface, on top of a napkin or tissue if you're worried about spilling, and waiting for the oil to be absorbed into the lava bead(s) before putting your jewelry on. This helps to keep the oil from getting on surrounding beads, which helps to prevent any possible staining.

For items with light colored lava beads, I recommend not using dark-colored oils with them, as they can very easily stain the beads.
